00:29:28,308 --> 00:29:29,184
<i>Tunggu.</i>

308
00:29:30,018 --> 00:29:33,438
Aku tak melihat luka bakar
di jasad-jasad itu.

309
00:29:34,189 --> 00:29:35,148
<i>Benar.</i>

310
00:29:35,940 --> 00:29:40,028
Mereka semua menunjukkan
ciri khas tubuh yang tenggelam.

311
00:29:40,987 --> 00:29:43,198
Entah apa yang sudah terjadi di sini.

312
00:29:44,199 --> 00:29:45,241
<i>Kapten Han,</i>

313
00:29:45,825 --> 00:29:48,286
jika kita tak bisa mengautopsi sekarang,

314
00:29:48,369 --> 00:29:52,665
