sampai misi selesai?

334
00:31:32,265 --> 00:31:33,141
Ya.

335
00:31:34,267 --> 00:31:36,269
Pasti mereka juga akan keberatan.

336
00:31:41,608 --> 00:31:43,234
Namun, kenapa kau…

337
00:31:45,820 --> 00:31:47,530
memintaku ikut misi ini?

338
00:31:58,458 --> 00:31:59,918
Kita sampai di Penyimpanan Satu.

339
00:32:08,968 --> 00:32:09,969
Berhasil.

340
00:32:10,053 --> 00:32:11,804
TUTUP

