00:32:12,805 --> 00:32:14,849
<i>Penyimpanan Dua, buka.</i>

343
00:32:20,521 --> 00:32:22,649
<i>Penyimpanan Satu, buka.</i>

344
00:32:34,494 --> 00:32:36,746
Kami masuk ke Penyimpanan Dua.

